a boiler room.

39:43.715 --> 39:44.948
It's not that hot, Lo.

39:45.049 --> 39:46.316
And the only time
I've seen you like this

39:46.318 --> 39:48.051
is when you used to
talk about...

39:48.720 --> 39:51.721
[chuckles] Holy shit!

39:52.624 --> 39:54.157
Andre is your "Dre."

39:54.259 --> 39:56.626
"Love of your life
from college" Dre, like...

39:57.529 --> 40:01.030
Mr. Might-ay, Might-ay!

40:01.032 --> 40:04.801
-[whispers] Yes.
-[chuckles]

40:05.804 --> 40:07.270
-Hi.
-Hey, hey.

40:07.272 --> 40:10.039
[chuckles] Mr. Watkins.

40:10.041 --> 40:12.809
Thank you again
for all of your hard work.

40:12.811 --> 40:14.944
-You have been a blessing.
-Just doing my job.

40:16.915 --> 40:17.947
Be there in a second.

40:19.451 --> 40:20.950
Hey, uh...

40:21.052 --> 40:23.319
My sister was right
to believe in you.

40:23.321 --> 40:24.521
And listen, I'm sorry

40:24.523 --> 40:25.822
I gave you such a hard time.

40:25.824 --> 40:28.024
You know, it's been
a lot to deal with.

40:28.026 --> 40:29.359
I'm just glad
the truth came out.

40:30.328 --> 40:32.829
"Love does not
delight in evil,

40:32.831 --> 40:34.831
but rejoices in the truth."

40:37.903 --> 40:39.536
Well, thank you
again, brother.
